name: dolomite production | dolomite | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/8284/documentation

This dataset is a weighted average from the respective regional datasets.;This dataset represents the production of 1 kg of dolomite from dolomite in ground, at the mine. Raw material, energy and water consumption, infrastructure for the site and machineries, land use, and emissions to air are a first approximation based on limestone production. The dataset includes raw materials, machineries, energy consumption, emissions to air, and infrastructure of the site. The dataset doesn't include emissions to water. An overall yield of 95% is assumed.;The main data source for this dataset is Althaus et al (2007).;References:;Althaus H.-J., Chudacoff M., Hischier R., Jungbluth N., Osses M. and Primas A. (2007) Life Cycle Inventories of Chemicals. ecoinvent report No. 8, v2.0. EMPA Dübendorf, Swiss Centre for Life Cycle Inventories, Dübendorf, CH.

The activity starts from dolomite in ground.

This activites ends with the production of 1 kg of dolomite. The dataset includes raw materials, machineries, energy consumption, emissions to air, and infrastructure of the site. The dataset doesn't include emissions to water.
category: B:Mining and quarrying/08:Other mining and quarrying/089:Mining and quarrying n.e.c./0891:Mining of chemical and fertilizer minerals
